<td style="padding:0;">Sample of "She's Lost Control", taken from the band's debut album <i>Unknown Pleasures</i> (1979). Curtis's baritone voice is accompanied by Hook's bass riff and Morris's drum beat, which was the result of producer Martin Hannett recording each part of the drumkit separately.</td>
